This project contains Ruby written package RPM specs that can be built against Ruby 1.9 and CentOS

### How to build

1. Install gcc-c++
2. Install rpm-build
3. Get imeyer/ruby-1.9.2-rpm , build Ruby 1.9 RPM and install it
4. cp SPECS/* and SOURCES/* to /usr/src/redhat/SPECS and /usr/src/redhat/SOURCES respectively
5. rpmbuild -bb SPEC/*.spec to build the RPMs

